At a glance license and code stats
Websocket connection between server and worker is pinged every 10 seconds, to avoid closing of inactive connections (#22)
Now using 'full-final-result' signal of gst-kaldi-nnet2-online (upgrade needed). Also fixed https://github.com/alumae/kaldi-gstreamer-server/issues/17
Now using 'full-final-result' signal of gst-kaldi-nnet2-online (upgrade needed). Also fixed https://github.com/alumae/kaldi-gstreamer-server/issues/17
Added id to every JSON response that is sent back to client, and also 'segment' property for recognition results
Output directory is now created if it doesn't exist
Updated English online nnet example configuration file to use TEDLIUM acosutic models combined with a language model by Cantab Research
Old decoder hung after first request; should be fixed https://github.com/alumae/kaldi-gstreamer-server/issues/10
Fixed error reporting of the HTTP interface
Note about ws4py 3.5.0 not working correctly
Fixed error of the HTTP interface caused by worker sending the adaptation state
Improved error handling in decoder2 and worker
Added a check to end endless loop that sometimes occurs in corner cases
Added support for sending and receiving adaptation state. Requires recent gst-kaldi-nnet2-online
Made more robust against against sleeping clients and client disconnects
got rid of a slow loop
